Make a content management system

node.js, Inquirer, MySql all used

npm i inquirer@8.2.4
walkthrough video

What do they want?
To view and edit departments, roles, and employee dbs

inquirer asks user:
--choice: view all departments, view all roles, view all employees, add a department, --add a role, add an employee, and update an employee role

----view all departments:
-------formatted table{department names and department ids}

----view all roles:
-------table{job title, role id, the department that role belongs to, and the salary for that role}

----view all employees:
-------table{including employee ids, first names, last names, job titles, departments, salaries, and managers that the employees report to}

----add a department:
-----enter name of new department:
-----------value is inserted into table (id auto gen)
